      <div xml:id="timf-glob">
        <head xml:id="timf-glob-Hd1e109">Gloria bona</head>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e111" n="a">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e113">Gloria est frequens de aliquo fama cum laude.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e115">Augustinus de diffinicionibus.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e118" n="b">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e120">Puritatis intime bono gloriari non potest ueraciter, nisi qui extrinsecus gloriolas
            perfecte respuerit. Nec enim pure ualet Dei uel proximi querere lucra, qui propria non
            contempserit.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e122">Bernardus in epistola.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e125" n="c">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e127">Si gloriari cupis, gloriam despice, et omnibus eris gloriosior.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e129">Crisostomus omelia IIII.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e132" n="d">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e134">Magna est eius gloria, qui nullis laudibus crescit, et nullius uituperacione
            minuitur.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e136">Cassiodorus in quadam epistola.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e140" n="e">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e142">Gloria est alicuius magnifici uel bone artis late patens preconium. Et ut perhibent
            qui de magnis maiora loquntur, secundam uitam dat gloria.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e144">Tullius in rethorica.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e147" n="f">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e149">Si quis tamen ad gloriam assequendam laborat, talem se efficiat qualis uult haberi.
            Quod si ostentacionem inani et ficto sermone uel uultu stabilem se gloriam assequi
            opinatur, uehementer errat. Vera enim gloria radices agit, ficta autem omnia celeriter
            tanquam flosculi decidunt, neque simulatum quicquam potest esse diuturnum.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e151">Ibidem.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e154" n="g">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e156">Expedita et compendiaria uia eos ad gloriam peruenire, Socrates dicebat, qui id
            agerent ut quales uideri uellent, tales eciam essent. Qua quidem predicacione aperte
            monebat, ut homines ipsam pocius uirtutem haurirent, quam umbram eius
            consectarentur.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e158">Valerius Maximus libro VII.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e161" n="h">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e163">Paterna namque gloria nos reddit inglorios, cum ab eius uestigiis dissimilitudine
            resilimus.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e165">Seneca.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e168" n="i">
          <quote xml:id="timf-glob-Qd1e170">Heu, quam difficilis glorie custodia est!</quote>
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e172">Seneca in prouerbiis.</ref>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="timf-glob-d1e175" n="ubi">
          <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e177">Contemptus k</ref>; <ref xml:id="timf-glob-Rd1e179">Humilitas u</ref>. </p>
      </div>
